ls2 =  \n| goals3 =  \n| goals4 =  \n| goals5 =  1  \n| goals6 =  0  \n| goals7 =  9  \n| goals8 =  0  \n| goals9 =  11  \n| goals10 =  2  \n| goals11 =  7  \n| goals12 =  14  \n| goals13 =  0  \n| goals14 =  2  \n| goals15 =  6 \n| goals16 =  9  \n| goals17 =  1\n| pcupdate       = 7 November 2013\n}}\n\n'''Piotr Rocki''' (born January 11, 1974 in [[Warsaw]]) is a [[Poland|Polish]] [[Association football|football]] player who plays for [[Kolejarz Str\u00f3\u017ce]].\n\n==Career==\nOn May 5, 2008 he joined [[KP Legia Warsaw]]. Before he played for Polonez Warsaw, Marcovia Marki, [[Polonia Warsaw]], [[Hetman Zamo\u015b\u0107]], [[G\u00f3rnik Zabrze]], [[Odra Wodzis\u0142aw \u015al\u0105ski]] and lately for [[Dyskobolia Grodzisk Wielkopolski]].\n\nFor Odra, he played 75 matches scoring 18 goals, becoming a fan favorite.\n\nRight Before the 2008/2009 season he joined Legia Warsaw. During his 2nd match for Legia, Rocki scored the winning goal for his team in the [[Polish SuperCup]] against Wis\u0142a Krak\u00f3w on July 20, 2008.\n\nAfter the 2008/09 season he joined a [[Polish First League]] club [[Podbeskidzie Bielsko-Bia\u0142a]]. Now he plays in [[Polonia Bytom]].<ref>[http://www.90minut.pl/news/227/news2272806-Trzech-nowych-pilkarzy-w-Polonii-Bytom.html Trzech nowych pi\u0142karzy w Polonii Bytom], 90minut.pl, 2014-01-23 {{in lang|pl}}</ref>\n\n== Achievements ==\n* [[Polish Cup]] -[[Dyskobolia Grodzisk Wielkopolski]] (2006/07 season)\n* Polish Ekstraklasa Cup - [[Dyskobolia Grodzisk Wielkopolski]] (2006/07 season)\n* Polish Ekstraklasa Cup- [[Dyskobolia Grodzisk Wielkopolski]] (2007/08 season)\n* [[Polish SuperCup]] - [[KP Legia Warsaw]] (2008/09 season)\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{90minut|1793}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rocki, Piotr}}\n[[Category:1974 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Polish footballers]]\n[[Category:Polonia Warsaw players]]\n[[Category:Legia Warsaw players]]\n[[Category:Dyskobolia Grodzisk Wielkopolski player