{"title_page": "Piotr Misztal (footballer)", "text_new": "{{About||the Polish politician|Piotr Misztal}}\n{{short description|Polish footballer}}\n\n'''Piotr Misztal''' (born July 10, 1987) is a Polish footballer ([[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]]) playing currently for [[Korona Kielce]]. In the hierarchy of goalkeepers he is third [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] in [[Korona Kielce]] squad.\n\nMisztal has made one [[Ekstraklasa]] appearance for Korona Kielce.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=90 Minut|title=Piotr Misztal|url=http://www.90minut.pl/kariera.php?id=7513|language=Polish|accessdate=2010-03-03}}</ref>\n\n== Clubs ==\n* 2005 {{flagicon|Poland}} [[Olimpia Warszawa]]\n* 2006 {{flagicon|Poland}} [[Korona Kielce]] (often reserve team)\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Misztal, Piotr}}\n[[Category:Polish footballers]]\n[[Category:Korona Kielce players]]\n[[Category:1987 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Association football goalkeepers]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Warsaw]]\n\n\n{{Poland-footy-goalkeeper-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Polish footballer}}\n{{About||the Polish politician|Piotr Misztal}}\n\n'''Piotr Misztal''' (born July 10, 1987) is a Polish footballer ([[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]]) playing currently for [[Korona Kielce]]. In the hierarchy of goalkeepers he is third [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] in [[Korona Kielce]] squad.\n\nMisztal has made one [[Ekstraklasa]] appearance for Korona Kielce.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=90 Minut|title=Piotr Misztal|url=http://www.90minut.pl/kariera.php?id=7513|language=Polish|accessdate=2010-03-03}}</ref>\n\n== Clubs ==\n* 2005 {{flagicon|Poland}} [[Olimpia Warszawa]]\n* 2006 {{flagicon|Poland}} [[Korona Kielce]] (often reserve team)\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Misztal, Piotr}}\n[[Category:Polish footballers]]\n[[Category:Korona Kielce players]]\n[[Category:1987 births]]\n[[Category:Living peopl